### ============================================================================
### Health Check Endpoints
### ============================================================================

### Detailed health check with model status
GET http://localhost:8000/health
Accept: application/json

### ============================================================================
### PDF Extraction Endpoints
### ============================================================================

### Convert PDF to markdown
POST http://localhost:8000/extract-pdf
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary

------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="example.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< example.pdf
------WebKitFormBoundary--

### ============================================================================
### Markdown File Processing Endpoints
### ============================================================================

### Upload markdown file to default collection
POST http://localhost:8000/process-markdown-file?collection_name=example
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary

------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="example.md"
Content-Type: text/markdown

< example.md
------WebKitFormBoundary--

### Upload markdown file to custom collection
POST http://localhost:8000/process-markdown-file?collection_name=my_collection
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary

------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="example.md"
Content-Type: text/markdown

< example.md
------WebKitFormBoundary--

### ============================================================================
### Search Endpoints
### ============================================================================

### Basic search with default collection and limit
POST http://localhost:8000/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "What is machine learning?",
  "limit": 5
}

### Search with custom limit
POST http://localhost:8000/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "How does deep learning work?",
  "limit": 10
}

### Search with specific collection
POST http://localhost:8000/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "Explain neural networks",
  "collection_name": "research_papers",
  "limit": 15
}

### Search in markdown document collection
POST http://localhost:8000/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "sample document",
  "collection_name": "my_collection",
  "limit": 5
}

### ============================================================================
### cURL Commands for Terminal
### ============================================================================

### Health check
curl http://localhost:8000/health

### Extract PDF to markdown (replace /path/to/document.pdf with actual path)
curl -X POST http://localhost:8000/extract-pdf \
  -F "file=@/path/to/document.pdf"

### Upload markdown file to default collection
curl -X POST "http://localhost:8000/process-markdown-file?collection_name=documents" \
  -F "file=@document.md"

### Upload markdown file to custom collection
curl -X POST "http://localhost:8000/process-markdown-file?collection_name=my_collection" \
  -F "file=@/path/to/document.md"

### Basic search
curl -X POST http://localhost:8000/search \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"query": "What is machine learning?"}'

### Search with custom limit and collection
curl -X POST http://localhost:8000/search \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"query": "Explain neural networks", "collection_name": "research_papers", "limit": 15}'

### Search in markdown collection
curl -X POST http://localhost:8000/search \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"query": "sample document", "collection_name": "my_collection", "limit": 5}'
